description:
Great British Menu - Season 12, Episodes 26 to 30

This week is the Wales regional heat and two determined newcomers, Paul Croasdale and Nick Brodie, take on returning chef to the competition Phil Carmichael for a place in the national finals. It is Phil's third time in the competition and this year he is determined to make it to the banquet. Phil, executive chef at Berners Tavern in London, is under pressure to impress as he is competing against his former head chef Paul.




Original Air Dates: 05-Jun-2017 to 09-Jun-2017
